	<p>Obesity Medicine is new specialty that is governed and credentialed through the American Board of Obesity Medicine (link to www.abom.org).  Organizations that provide educational support and recognition to the field of Obesity Medicine can be found here (link to www.abom.org â€“ lower page for supporting organizations).</p>
	<p>An Obesity Medicine trained physician will not only help you to lose weight but will be an expert in recognizing and treating your weight related conditions.  This is important because as you lose weight, your medications that you have been taking for your weight related condition will frequently change.</p>
	<p>Common problems that are seen in an obesity medicine clinic can include but are not limited to:</p>
